{"questionId":"6057","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The following data apply to the star Gacrux.</p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage mjpage__block\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\" alttext=\"\\begin{array}{*{20}{l}}  {{\\text{Radius}}}&amp;{ = 58.5 \\times {{10}^9}{\\text{ m}}} \\\\   {{\\text{Temperature}}}&amp;{ = 3600{\\text{ K}}} \\\\   {{\\text{Distance}}}&amp;{ = 88{\\text{ ly}}}  \\end{array}\">\n  <mtable columnalign=\"left\" rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>Radius</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>58.5</mn>\n          <mo>×</mo>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mn>10</mn>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>9</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>&nbsp;m</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>Temperature</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>3600</mn>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>&nbsp;K</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n    <mtr>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>Distance</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n      <mtd>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mn>88</mn>\n          <mrow>\n            <mtext>&nbsp;ly</mtext>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mtd>\n    </mtr>\n  </mtable>\n</math></span></p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>The luminosity of the Sun <em>L</em><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"_ \\odot \">\n  <msub>\n    <mi></mi>\n    <mo>⊙</mo>\n  </msub>\n</